MALACAÑANG Manila

PROCLAMATION NO. 254

RESERVING FOR SCHOOL SITE PURPOSES OF THE CAMIGUIN COLLEGE OF FISHERIES AND MARITIME STUDIES CERTAIN PARCELS OF LAND OF THE PUBLIC DOMAIN SITUATED IN THE MUNICIPALITY OF MAMBAJAO, PROVINCE OF CAMIGUIN, ISLAND OF CAMIGUIN.

Upon recommendation of Secretary of Environment and Natural Resources and by virtue of the power vested in me by law, I, CORAZON C. AQUINO, President of the Philippines, do hereby withdraw from sale and settlement and reserve for school site purposes of the Camiguin College of Fisheries and Maritime Studies, subject to private rights, if any there be, certain parcels of land of the public domain situated in the municipality of Mambajao, Province of Camiguin, Island of Camiguin, and more particularly described as follows:

Lot 2, Ccs-10-000080-D

A PARCEL OF LAND (Lot 2, Ccs-10-000080-D), situated in Poblacion, Municipality of Mambajao, Province of Camiguin, Island of Camiguin, Bounded on the W., along line 1-2 by Lot 981; along line 2-3 by Lot 441; along line 3-4 by Lot 440; along line 4-5 by Lot 439; and along line 5-6 by Lot 430; all of Cad-473, Mambajao Cadastre; on the NW., along lines 6-7-8 by Lot 429, along line 8-9 by Lot 974, along line 9-10 by Lot 988 and along line 10-11 by Lot 398, all of Cad-473, Mambajao Cadastre; on the N., along line 11-12 by Lot 399, along line 12-13 by Lot 400, along line 13-14 by Lot 403, along line 14-15 by Lot 405, and along line 15-16 by Lot 406, all of Cad-473, Mambajao Cadastre; on the E., along lines 16-17-18 by Balintawak Creek; on the S., along line 18-19 by Lot 1, Ccs-10-000080-D; on the SW., along line 19-20 by Lot 451, along line 20-21 by Lot 450 and along line 21-1 by Lot 442, all of Cad-473, Mambajao Cadastre. Beginning at a point marked “1” of Lot 2, Ccs-10-000080-A, being N. 50-34′ E., 413.20 m. from B.L.L.M. # 1, Cad-473, Mambajao Cadastre.

